mplicated in a match-fixing scandal involving Chinese business executive [[Zheyun Ye]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[International Herald Tribune]]|title=Roundup: Belgian police raid match-fixing targets|url=http://www.iht.com/articles/2006/03/16/sports/WORLD-5853123.php|date=2006-03-17|accessdate=2008-11-18}}</ref>\n\n==Club career==\nSuray had a spell in the Turkish [[Super Lig]] with [[Altay S.K.]] and [[Adanaspor]]<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Turkish Football Federation]]|title=OLIVIER MARCEL GHISLAIN SURAY|url=http://www.tff.org/Default.aspx?pageId=526&kisiId=29541|accessdate=2008-11-18}}</ref> and several seasons in the [[Belgian First Division]] with [[R. Charleroi S.C.]], [[R.S.C. Anderlecht]] and [[R.A.E.C. Mons]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Voetbal International|title=Olivier Suray|url=http://www.vi.nl/Spelers/Speler/OlivierSuray.htm|accessdate=2008-11-18}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://guardian.touch-line.com/StatsCentre.asp?CTID=57&CPID=120&TEID=1403&PLID=49057&pStr=Player Guardian's Stats Centre] {{dead link|date=April 2020}}\n* {{FootballDatabase.eu|32831<!-- -olivier-suray -->}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2011}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Suray, Olivier}}\n[[Category:1971 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Belgian footballers]]\n[[Category:Belgian football managers]]\n[[Category:R. Charleroi S.C. players]]\n[[Category:R.S.C. Anderlecht players]]\n[[Category:Standard Li\u00e8ge players]]\n[[Category:R.A.A. Louvi\u00e9roise players]]\n[[Category:K.S.K. Beveren players]]\n[[Category:R.A.E.C. Mons players]]\n[[Category:Altay S.K. footballers]]\n[[Category:Adanaspor footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople involved in betting scandals]]\n[[Category:People from Namur (city)]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n\n\n{{Belgium-footy-defender-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Belgian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Olivier Suray\n| 